{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_019UkTQVUhsRnQoqp3NECuQW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01BiYNHFaYLd6uM9iitioKQo","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git add src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates.rs && git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\ntest(0.7.0): Pack 2 RED — re-pin AC-013 to 80/300 ms; add AC-013b recall@10 floor\n\nRe-pin AC013_BUDGET_P50/P99 from 50/200 ms to 80/300 ms per the\nHITL-locked Pack 2 target (bit-KNN + f32 rerank). Canonical-CI N=1M\non the f32-brute-force read path measured p50=2048 ms / p99=2327 ms\n(dev/plans/runs/0.7.0-PERF-EXP-W4.1-ac013-canonical-output.json), so\nthe new budget is RED at canonical scale until P2-IMPL lands. Dev-box\nN=10K smoke remains GREEN (p50=8 ms / p99=13 ms).\n\nAdd ac_013b_recall_at_10_floor: reuses seed_ac013_corpus and\nac013_query_bodies, computes brute-force f32 ground truth via a raw\nread-only rusqlite::Connection on engine.path() (same SQL as\nlib.rs:2317-2342), compares against engine.search().results, and\nasserts mean recall@10 >= 0.90 (HITL floor; see\ndev/plans/0.7.0-HITL-recommendations.md:89 and\nADR-0.7.0-vector-binary-quant section 2). Pre-Pack-2-IMPL recall = 1.0\nbecause production path == ground-truth path; the test is the\ncanonical regression gate for the P2-IMPL rewrite.\n\nTests-only slice. No production code changes. AGENT_LONG-gated to\nmatch AC-013.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1 | tail -15","description":"Commit after rustfmt"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4492,"cache_read_input_tokens":76039,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4492},"output_tokens":47,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"878701b8-da54-4